            "text": "<p>Good light is the biggest factor in beautiful engagement ring photos.</p><p>Some of the best lighting suggestions are ensuring that your setting has soft natural light pouring in or a cloudy day or you are positioned near a window. It is important that you avoid direct sunlight or yellow indoor lights because they will create a glare, taking away the beauty of the ring.</p>",
