            "text": "<p>Here are some natural poses that work for every style of engagement ring poses.<br/>Resting your hand on a soft surface so that your hands look relaxed .<br/>Holding your partners hand is always the perfect pose for sweet engagement ring couple photos.Holding a coffee mug or bouquet adds texture and dimension to your ring pic without distracting from the ring.</p>",
