            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Add_Your_Partner_for_Cute_Couple_Shots.png",
            "text": "<p>Your story becomes more meaningful when the photo includes both of you. Try:<br/>1]Interlocked fingers<br/>2]Your hand on their chest<br/>3]Them holding your hand from below<br/><br/>These are perfect couple ring poses and ring ceremony engagement couple poses that feel natural and genuine.</p>",
