          }
        },
        "image_with_text_jBpirK": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Capture_the_Ring_in_Action_8de68172-e2c2-4750-bef9-95dc48c1663b.png",
            "text": "<p>Instead of staged shots, try action moments. This makes your engagement ring pics feel authentic. Some shots you can take for these candid-like moments are pouring coffee, holding a flower, flipping through a book, cheering with drinks or even just simply walking with your partner. </p><p>These moments are perfect for engagement ring photo ideas.</p>",
